==食物腐败==
{{expand section|date=July 2015}}
因为具有多种多样的代谢特征，能够在低温和特殊环境下生存，很多假单胞菌都能够导致食物腐败。典型的例子有：{{Tsl|en|Pseudomonas fragi|莓实假单胞菌|莓实假单胞菌}}可以引起奶制品腐坏,<ref>{{cite journal |author=Pereira, JN |author2=Morgan, ME |last-author-amp=yes |title=Nutrition and physiology of ''Pseudomonas fragi'' |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_1957-12_74_6/page/710 |journal=J Bacteriol |volume=74 |issue=6 |pages=710–3 |date=Dec 1957  |pmid=13502296 |pmc=289995 }}</ref>，{{Tsl|en|Pseudomonas taetrolens|腐臭假单胞菌|腐臭假单胞菌}}和{{Tsl|en|Pseudomonas mucidolens|霉味假单胞菌|霉味假单胞菌}}能够造成鸡蛋腐臭，<ref>{{cite journal |author=Levine, M |author2=Anderson, DQ |last-author-amp=yes |title=Two New Species of Bacteria Causing Mustiness in Eggs |journal=J Bacteriol |volume=23 |issue=4 |pages=337–47 |date=Apr 1932  |pmid=16559557 |pmc=533329 }}</ref>{{Tsl|en|Pseudomonas lundensis|隆德假单胞菌|隆德假单胞菌}}，能够造成牛奶、奶酪、肉类和鱼类的腐败。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Gennari, M |author2=Dragotto, F |last-author-amp=yes |title=A study of the incidence of different fluorescent ''Pseudomonas'' species and biovars in the microflora of fresh and spoiled meat and fish, raw milk, cheese, soil and water |journal=J Appl Bacteriol |volume=72 |issue=4 |pages=281–8 |date=Apr 1992  |pmid=1517169 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2672.1992.tb01836.x }}</ref>

